</LG>
<LG>
<PB N="22" REF="65">
<L><NOTE N="a" PLACE="foot"><HI>Lewis the Holy,</HI> who went on the fir&s;t Royal Expedition to the <HI>Holy Land,</HI> and lo&s;t his Army there, in fighting with the <HI>Saracens,</HI> where our Great <HI>Richard,</HI> Duke of <HI>Cornwall,</HI> al&s;o lo&s;t his Life.</NOTE> His Ance&s;tor, whom Mony made a Saint,</L>
<L>And Legends full of Lyes his Glories paint,</L>
