<L>With Homage Lower <HI>than his Vanity could e're</HI> expect;</L>
<L>Tell him to Rule by Law's to rule by Halves,</L>
<L>And <HI>own them&s;elves</HI> his Cattle and his Slaves;</L>
<L><HI>Pray, cant, and &s;wear,</HI> exotic Ways contrive,</L>
<L>To make <HI>their Bubl'd Prince</HI> the Fraud believe;</L>
<L>Bind their di&s;&s;embl'd Homage to the Crown,</L>
<L>And bend the <HI>Solemns of Religion</HI> down;</L>
