Call in the Sacred to uphold the Cheat,</L>
<L>And make the<NOTE N="a" PLACE="foot">An Oath is call'd a Sacrament in other Languages, and the Sacra|ment here is frequently made u&s;e of as an Oath, and as a Bond of Sin|cerity.</NOTE> Sacrament confederate;</L>
<L>Join Heaven and Hell in one united Crime,</L>
<L>And mix th' Infernal up with the Sublime:</L>
