</LG>
<LG>
<L><HI>C&mdash;on</HI> with Eccle&s;ia&s;tick Dignity,</L>
<L>Supports the Regal Power, and<NOTE N="a" PLACE="foot">He gave the Lye by his Practice to all tho&s;e former Prie&s;ts that had rais'd the Power of Eccle&s;ia&s;tick Authority for he ab&s;olutely &s;ub|mitted it all to the Regal Dignity and Divine Right of the Prince.</NOTE> <HI>gives the Lye;</HI></L>
