<L>And took tho&s;e Oaths <HI>he knew he</HI><NOTE N="b" PLACE="foot">They that took this ab&s;olute Oath, knew when they took it, they were not able to keep what they &s;wore, if they were put to the extremi|ty; and &s;o it a&s;terwards appear'd.</NOTE> <HI>cou'd not keep:</HI></L>
