<LG>
<L><HI>Had he been faithful</HI> to his Sovereign Lord,</L>
<L>And fought him with <HI>the Weapons of the Word;</HI></L>
<L>Had he <HI>with Hone&s;t Duty</HI> fir&s;t appeal'd,</L>
