<LG>
<L><HI>William</HI> was<NOTE N="b" PLACE="foot"><HI>William</HI> the <HI>Conqueror,</HI> might be call'd a U&s;urper, but he was no Tyrant at fir&s;t, till he had &s;ecured the Po&s;&s;e&s;&s;ion to him&s;elf, and intirely &s;ubdued all his Enemies, then he began to &s;how him&s;elf.</NOTE> yet no Tyrant, had not took</L>
